:''Not to be confused with [[Thû]].''
'''''tû''''' is a [[Noldorin]] word meaning "muscle, sinew; vigour, physical strength".<ref name=LR>{{LR|Etymologies}}, p. 394</ref>

Retaining the same form and meaning, ''tû'' is commonly considered a valid [[Neo-Elvish|Neo-Sindarin]] word.<ref>{{HM|GS}}, p. 290</ref><ref>[[Didier Willis]], [http://www.jrrvf.com/hisweloke/sindar/online/english.html Hiswelókë's Sindarin Dictionary] at [http://www.jrrvf.com/hisweloke/sindar/index.html Jrrvf.com] (accessed 9 December 2011)</ref><ref>[[Helge Fauskanger]], "[http://folk.uib.no/hnohf/parviphith.doc ''Parviphith Edhellen'': Sindarin Wordlist]" at [http://folk.uib.no/hnohf/ Ardalambion] (accessed 9 December 2011)</ref>
